snippet: LEAD: A plan to give California one of the nation's earliest Presidential primaries has been defeated, with lawmakers unable to agree whether to prohibit referendums from any Presidential ballot....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: A plan to give California one of the nation's earliest Presidential primaries has been defeated, with lawmakers unable to agree whether to prohibit referendums from any Presidential ballot.

headline.main: California Lawmakers Defeat Plan for Early Presidential Primary
